meta.@content: Model of a Typhoon Eurofighter, Open the dome by touching, Airplane is tilted to the left side. To implement it rotate on the x-axis 90 degrees clockwise
FIS bases on Kyle Pearson, online url: http://www.rccad.com/Gallery/Vrml/EuroFighter.wrl. Sounds are self created
